videos.headline: Jalen Pickett's bucket beats the shot clock
videos.description: Jalen Pickett gets the layup to fall for Penn State right before the shot clock expires.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Jalen Pickett's bucket beats the shot clock) 2023/3/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sir'Jabari Rice sinks a Texas 3-pointer
videos.description: Sir'Jabari Rice increases Texas' lead over Penn State with his 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Sir'Jabari Rice sinks a Texas 3-pointer) 2023/3/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State takes advantage of Texas' errant pass in the back court
videos.description: Seth Lundy takes the ball to the other end of the court for a Penn State layup.

videos.headline: Dylan Disu puts Texas on his back down the stretch
videos.description: Dylan Disu helps Texas secure a win over Penn State as the Longhorns advance to the Sweet 16 for the first time since 2008.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Dylan Disu puts Texas on his back down the stretch) 2023/3/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dylan Disu ends Penn State's 10-0 run with his layup
videos.description: Dylan Disu cuts into Penn State's lead over Texas with his layup in the second half.
